          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">While selecting targets for this unit&apos;s Storm Eagle Rocket (1 &amp; 2, 3 or 4), if you have no ready units except units with Artillery Support, you may ‘call for an artillery strike’. If you do, you may instead target an enemy unit within 24&quot; of and visible to any of your infantry units within 24&quot; of this unit. Additionally, for each attack made for that weapon this turn, add 1 to the Hit Roll of that attack.</characteristic>
