          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Psychic Power" typeId="9060-973c-99e9-75b4">After this unit makes a Psychic Test, if that Psychic Test had two or more dice with the same result, this unit suffers D3 SW, the nearest visible enemy unit with 24” suffers 2D3 SW and this unit gains Psyker 3. Then, this unit may make a Psychic Test.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile typeId="55da-e0a0-1fa3-2d1c" typeName="Leader" hidden="false" id="6cbb-b815-c368-b4c3">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Must Attach to" typeId="2c63-5e3f-9132-459d">This unit must attach to:
a) Any Troops unit
This unit may only Cast psychic powers from the ‘Psychic Powers of the Battle Psykers’ table.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
      </profiles>
      <selectionEntries>
        <selectionEntry type="upgrade" import="true" name="Psychic Powers" hidden="false" id="c5ed-adde-d072-fc2e">
