          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">For each Resolve Test made by a friendly infantry unit within 12” of this unit, reroll a 1 for that Resolve Test.</characteristic>
          </characteristics>
        </profile>
        <profile name="Summary Execution" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="8197-c744-f01b-ab33">
          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After this unit’s Move step, you may select one of your infantry units within 8” of and visible to this unit with Suppressed X. Then, one model from that unit dies. Then, roll 2D3 and reduce its Suppressed X by the result.</characteristic>
