  <sharedProfiles>
    <profile name="Recrew" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="9567-753f-2da2-e85a">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">After one of your friendly infantry units finishes an Advance within 1” of this unit, you may remove up to 10 models from that unit. If you do, this unit Heals 1 for each model removed.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
    <profile name="Entrench" typeId="e9b6-89e0-ffee-5662" typeName="Ability" hidden="false" id="57ea-cdf2-571a-71ad">
      <characteristics>
        <characteristic name="Description:" typeId="22b9-735d-71b1-6d7a">For each ranged attack that targets this unit, add 1 to the Saving Throw of that attack. After a Move Roll made for this unit during its Move step, you may discard the highest result of that Move Roll. If you do not, this unit loses this ability until after the next time it’s Activated.</characteristic>
      </characteristics>
    </profile>
  </sharedProfiles>
